> empty commands.
>=20
> =
http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799.2013edition/utilities/V3_c=
hap02.html#tag_18_10
>=20
> The prompt I have used since about 1997 (and I can't remember where I =
got
> it from - somewhere on Usenet, probably) in its most distilled form is
>=20
> :;
>=20
> although in practice I have a load of extra fluff for username, =
hostname,
> CWD, etc. usw.
>=20
> Tony.
