&nbsp;10th edition Unix and Plan 9 rc both have ('% ' ' ') as the =
&nbsp;&nbsp;<br class=3D"">default value of $prompt. &nbsp;At least =
that's how it's described in the<br class=3D"">manual. &nbsp;None of the =
